KODI Popcorn Time
=================

What it is
----------
With KODI Popcorn Time you can search for movies that you can see immediately in KODI.

Download
--------
Check out https://github.com/markop159/KODI-Popcorn-Time/tree/master/Releases to download the ZIP file.

Supported Platforms
-------------------
* XBMC/KODI 13.x and later
* Windows x32 and x64
* OSX x32 and x64
* Linux x32, x64 and ARM
* Android ARM 4.0+
* Darwin x64
* Raspberry Pi

Discussions/Proposals
---------------------
Proposals may be posted under https://github.com/markop159/KODI-Popcorn-Time/issues.

Issues
------
Please, file an issue :) - https://github.com/markop159/KODI-Popcorn-Time/issues

Credits
-------
* Fixed KODI Popcorn Time add-on from https://github.com/Diblo/KODI-Popcorn-Time
* KODI Popcorn Time is a rewrite of http://github.com/steeve/xbmctorrent.
* http://github.com/steeve/libtorrent-go
* http://github.com/steeve/torrent2http

